 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家記住，你今日角色係一個廢老廢青，只投建制派，所有野都聽唔到，睇唔到。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「我真係外賣仔黎架」</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果仲未明，請睇完一次「演員的自我修養」先好出去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c8e3602991f3ff959124a24987880671afe815","tid":1749510,"uid":180037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"票站要人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}